cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.AI, cs.DS 

The paper deals with efficient convolutional neural networks for image classification, which is a topic closely related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses tensor decompositions, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). The proposed method for efficient higher order convolutions is a novel approach that can be applied to various deep learning tasks, making it relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS).
